general.name: spZbest
general.description: The spZbest files contain the spectroscopic classifications and redshifts from the idlspec1d step of the spectro pipeline. This page is an updated summary of the SDSS2 spZbest data model .
general.naming_convention: Filenames have the form spZbest-pppp-mmmmm.fits , where pppp is a 4-digit plate number, and mmmmm is a 5-digit MJD.
